       <td bgcolor="#f1f1f1" style="font-weight:700" width="10%">营养含量</td>
       <td bgcolor="#f1f1f1" style="font-weight:700" width="10%">主要功效</td>
             </tr>
  <tr>
              <td bgcolor="#FFFFFF" style="color:#666" width="10%">96</td>
        <td bgcolor="#FFFFFF" style="color:#666" width="10%">锅</td>
        <td bgcolor="#FFFFFF" style="color:#666" width="10%">简单</td>
        <td bgcolor="#FFFFFF" style="color:#666" width="10%">15分钟</td>
        <td bgcolor="#FFFFFF" style="color:#666" width="10%">炒、煮</td>
        <td bgcolor="#FFFFFF" style="color:#666" width="10%">鲜</td>
        <td bgcolor="#FFFFFF" style="color:#666" width="10%">鱼含丰富优质蛋白</td>
        <td bgcolor="#FFFFFF" style="color:#666" width="10%">酸菜中的乳酸能开胃提神、醒酒去腻，还能能增进食欲、帮助消化；多吃鱼可以健康长寿。</td>
              </tr>
      </table>
        <p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><span style="background: white; color: #404040; font-size: 10.5pt"><img src="http://www.kakaxian.com/images/upload/Image/1mei.JPG" alt="" />鱼片用一茶匙</span><span style="background: white; color: #404040; font-size: 10.5pt">、白胡椒一茶匙、</span><span style="background: white; color: #404040; font-size: 10.5pt">蛋清半个</span><span style="background: white; color: #404040; font-size: 10.5pt">、干淀粉三茶匙腌渍，用手仔细反复抓拌均匀，静置</span><span style="background: white; color: #404040; font-size: 10.5pt">5-10</span><span style="background: white; color: #404040; font-size: 10.5pt">分钟；</span></p>
<p><span style="background: white; color: #404040; font-size: 10.5pt"><img alt="" width="184" height="112" src="http://www.kakaxian.com/images/upload/Image/s1.JPG" /></span></p>
<div style="line-height: 11pt; text-indent: -18pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt 18pt"><span style="background: white; color: #404040; font-size: 10.5pt"><img src="http://www.kakaxian.com/images/upload/Image/2mei.JPG" alt="" />锅里放油炒香葱姜蒜、野山椒、泡红椒，下入鱼骨炒一分钟；</span></div>
<div style="line-height: 11pt; text-indent: -18pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt 18pt"><span style="background: white; color: #404040; font-size: 10.5pt"><img alt="" width="184" height="113" src="http://www.kakaxian.com/images/upload/Image/s2.JPG" /></span></div>
<div style="line-height: 11pt; text-indent: -18pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt 18pt"><span style="background: white; color: #404040; font-size: 10.5pt"><img src="http://www.kakaxian.com/images/upload/Image/3mei.JPG" alt="" />放入酸菜继续炒一分钟；</span></div>
<div style="line-height: 11pt; text-indent: -18pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt 18pt"><span style="background: white; color: #404040; font-size: 10.5pt"><img alt="" width="184" height="113" src="http://www.kakaxian.com/images/upload/Image/s3.JPG" /></span></div>
<div style="line-height: 11pt; text-indent: -18pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt 18pt"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt"><img src="http://www.kakaxian.com/images/upload/Image/4mei.JPG" alt="" />加500g左右的开水（或清水）大火烧开</span>，<span style="background: white; color: #404040; font-size: 10.5pt">中火煮</span><span style="background: white; color: #404040; font-size: 10.5pt">20</span><span style="background: white; color: #404040; font-size: 10.5pt">分钟到鱼汤白。调入适量盐，把汤中料都捞出来铺在碗底。（各家吃盐大小不一样，一定要调自己的口味）。</span></div>
<div style="line-height: 11pt; text-indent: -18pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt 18pt"><span style="background: white; color: #404040; font-size: 10.5pt"><img alt="" width="184" height="113" src="http://www.kakaxian.com/images/upload/Image/s4.JPG" /></span></div>
<div style="line-height: 11pt; text-indent: -18pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt 18pt"><span style="background: white; color: #404040; font-size: 10.5pt"><img src="http://www.kakaxian.com/images/upload/Image/5mei.JPG" alt="" />锅大火烧鱼汤，鱼片一点点放入，晃动锅，最上面的鱼片</span><span style="background: white; color: #404040; font-size: 10.5pt">7</span><span style="background: white; color: #404040; font-size: 10.5pt">成熟捞出放在碗上面，倒入鱼汤即可。</span></div>
<div style="line-height: 11pt; text-indent: -18pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt 18pt"><span style="background: white; color: #404040; font-size: 10.5pt"><img alt="" width="303" height="257" src="http://www.kakaxian.com/images/upload/Image/s5.JPG" /></span></div>
<div style="line-height: 11pt; text-indent: -18pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt 18pt">&nbsp;</div>
<div style="line-height: 11pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt"><span style="font-size: small">菜品简介:</span></div>
<div style="line-height: 11pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt"><span style="font-size: small">此菜酸 鲜 爽 口，消 暑 解 腻的家庭版温情酸菜鱼烹制好啦！</span></div>       </blockquote>
